reviewText:
This would be a nice video if the patterns where included with it.  The patterns are something you have to buy separately.
This video is on a public broadcasting station for free.  So why buy it?  Wish I have found the site before I bought the video.
Just be aware that if you don't already have doll patterns, there are none with this video.  These patterns are to be purchased separately in a booklet???  It would have been so nice to have them available with the video.
